ally got together with my wife when she vomited down my back in a club.</li>\nShe got a police incidence number that night, with regards to an (almost) unrelated matter.\n	<li>sixth thing</li>\n	<li>I thought my Ph.D. <a title=\"Thesis Examinations - Wikipedia\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Thesis#Thesis_examinations\" target=\"_blank\"><em>viva</em></a> was going to be my hardest single day. Turns out I was wrong.</li>\nOn 18th August, 2005 I received the worst phone call of my life. It was my mother, to tell me that my brother had fallen into a ravine while walking in Northern Spain, and died. He was 29. His funeral was, and remains, the hardest day of my life.\n</ol>\nOutro\nNot passing it on, claim your tag in the comments, if you want...','7 \'interesting\' things',0,'','inherit','open','open','','73-revision-18','','','2009-01-13 22:22:27','2009-01-13 22:22:27','',73,'http://blog.fuzzierlogic.com/?p=92',0,'revision','',0),(93,2,'2009-01-13 22:22:29','2009-01-13 22:22:29','I\'ve been <a title=\"Memes - Wikipedia\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Meme\" target=\"_blank\">memed</a> by <a title=\"eridanus.net - 7 things\" href=\"http://eridanus.net/blog/?p=305\" target=\"_blank\">Dan</a>.\r\n\r\n<strong>The challenge</strong>\r\n\r\nWrite 7 interesting things about myself, and pass on the meme, chain letter stylee.\r\n\r\nSo here are 7 facts about me, my family and my life. Interesting-ness is in the eye of the beholder. I suspect its largely self-indulgent twaddle.\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>I got married over the anvil (actually <em>an</em> anvil, not <em>the</em> anvil - a wedding in the Blacksmith\'s is much more expensive) in <a title=\"Gretna Green - Wikipedia\" href=\"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gretna_Green\" target=\"_blank\">Gretna Green</a>, and we had paid the only guests (2 witnesses) to be there.</li>\r\nWe had been engaged for nearly 2 ½ years, with no hope of being able to afford a \'proper\' wedding in the forseeable future. We had joked about el